review: Doctor is very friendly and all doubts without any time constraints. She thoroughly analyzed the reports and advised satisfactorily for future course of actions in pregnancy.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
The diagnosis and the course of treatment was perfect
Very much satisfied with the consultation and the medication
I expected a physical checkup but none was done. The doctor maintained social distancing and gave me a lot of test and medicines. This is like video consultation only. Disappointed.
reply_text:
Sorry for disappointment.  
People with fever are not done physical examination.  You are right. Social distance is maintained.  It is the tests which will bring a diagnosis especially in case of fever.  COVID times are challenging.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: Didnt have a great experience. She dismissed my concerns completely once I mentioned anxiety issues and started talking and explaining the issues to my friend instead of me.
reply_text: I don't understand what is wrong in explaining your issues to the accompanying person? I remember explaining to you also and counseling you positively. I didn't dismiss your concerns

review:
Approachable, able to detect the cause of fever, appropriate medicine and tests given. 

Very cordial , good listener.
Consulting her for swollen lymph node. She is patient and kind. Her prescription and advice gave me so much relief and I am so much better now.
very true doctor is giving a ***t treatment also she have cured our problem of swollen lymph nodes very thankful to her very king answers every question

The experience with doctor went very well. However the receptionist handling could be handled better. there are 2 sofas in clinic, when I reached it was empty, 8 people can sit, receptionist was not comfortable taking me in, if patient alone was sitting at one sofa, I could have sat at other sofa alone till any patient came. However I was made stand in hot sun for 30 mins and because of this my health went down by evening. Rest all good.
